# Cargo performance default (marser)

When running Cargo commands in this repository (e.g. `cargo check`, `cargo run`, `cargo test`), always include **`--features parser-erased`** unless the user explicitly asks not to.

When running **`cargo run` / `cargo build` with `--example`**, include **`annotate-snippets`** as well (examples require it for `ParserError::eprint` and related APIs).

Examples:
```bash
cargo check --features parser-erased -q
cargo run --features "parser-erased annotate-snippets" -q --example mini_language -- <script.ml>
cargo test --features parser-erased -q
```